      <title>Wellness Wednesday In-Person Event: Progressive Muscle Relaxation  at Hilltop Lounge (Upper Level of Blackburn)</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<div>  <img src="https://localist-images.azureedge.net/photos/53169917016196/huge/cfae64200a3f8ca265bd8b13a2fb763813cb33b4.jpg" style="width: 100%;" />  <div style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;"><strong>Mon, 29 Jun 2026</strong></div>  <div><p>Wellness Wednesday In-Person Event: Progressive Muscle Relaxation</p>

<p>Progressive muscle relaxation (PMR) is a stress reduction technique designed to release muscle tension and relax the body and mind.  Developed by an American physician, it involves systematically tensing and relaxing specific muscle groups.  If you want a nourishing break from work, and to learn how to help shift the body from stress into calm, join us for this in-person Wellness Wednesday session.  Led by Howard’s Onsite Health Coach Katherine Smith, free yoga mats will be provided. Wear comfortable clothing!   </p>

<p> </p>

<p>📧 <a href="mailto:Katherine.Smith@Evernorth.com">Katherine.Smith@Evernorth.com</a> 
<br>📞 240-814-1343</p>

<p><a href="https://events.howard.edu/event/copy-of-wellness-wednesday-in-person-event-gentle-yoga">View on site</a> | <a href="mailto:?subject=I found an interesting event%3A Wellness Wednesday In-Person Event%3A Progressive Muscle Relaxation%C2%A0&amp;body=I found an interesting event you may like%3A%0A%0A%0ADate%3A Jun 29%2C 2026%0A%0ADescription%3A%0AWellness Wednesday In-Person Event%3A Progressive Muscle Relaxation%0A%0AProgressive muscle relaxation %28PMR%29 is a stress reduction technique designed to release muscle tension and relax the body and mind.  Developed by an American physician%2C it involves systematically tensing and relaxing specific muscle groups.  If you want a nourishing break from work%2C and to learn how to help shift the body from stress into calm%2C join us for this in-person Wellness Wednesday session.  Led by Howard%E2%80%99s Onsite Health Coach Katherine Smith%2C free yoga mats will be provided. Wear comfortable clothing%21   %0A%0A %0A%0A%F0%9F%93%A7 Katherine.Smith%40Evernorth.com %0A%F0%9F%93%9E 240-814-1343%0A%0Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fevents.howard.edu%2Fevent%2Fcopy-of-wellness-wednesday-in-person-event-gentle-yoga%0A">Email this event</a></p></div></div>]]></description>
